member.example:
The code below shows the defition of a data view and the corresponding SQL query.
public PXSelect<Table1, Where<Table1.field1, IsNotNull, And<Not<Table1.field2, Equal<Zero>>>>> records;
SELECT * FROM Table1 WHERE ( Table1.Field1 IS NOT NULL AND NOT (Table1.Field2 = 0) )

The code below shows the defition of a data view and the corresponding SQL query.
public PXSelect<Table1, Where<Table1.field1, IsNotNull, And<Not<Table1.field2, Equal<Zero>, Or<Table1.field2, Greater<Table1.field1>>>>>> records;
SELECT * FROM Table1 WHERE ( Table1.Field1 IS NOT NULL AND NOT (Table1.Field2 = 0 OR Table1.Field2 > Table1.Field1) )

