member.summary:
For a DAC, the attribute specifies graphs and corresponding conditions;
            the first graph whose condition is met will be used to edit DAC's records.
            For a graph, the attribute specifies DACs and corresponding conditions;
            records of the first DAC whose condition is met will be edited by the graph.

